An experimental animated ribbon which reveals a curtain content.

== Description ==

An experimental animated ribbon which reveals a curtain content.

Curious about how this looks in action? [Check out the demo page](http://lab.hakim.se/forkit-js/).

Based on [forkit.js](https://github.com/hakimel/forkit.js) by Hakim El Hattab.

